{"tid":225133,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[酒撚] 邊到學雞尾酒好？","createTime":"2017-05-01T14:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:13.000Z","uid":58625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5f25ba7a458061969558e448d3cae32fbc0fe4","tid":225133,"uid":58625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n鐘意飲雞尾酒，所以想上堂學多啲有關雞尾酒嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c064521a0294c497fcfe866a4963876ff776884c","tid":225133,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題<br />\n鐘意飲雞尾酒，所以想上堂學多啲有關雞尾酒嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀有間雞尾酒學校, 無論係工具定課程都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有心做bartender嘅去酒吧見工可能好啲<br />\n自娛嘅去圖書館借幾本書同上網啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順便講吓, 有本漫畫叫《王牌酒保》, 用雞尾酒同日本酒吧文化做題材, 睇過覺得本嘢真係有啲料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近續篇仲出咗中文版<br />\n<br />\n利申: 自娛"},{"pid":"2aa13d7fa121ca67244309e61c6f86f9765a9ce7","tid":225133,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"其實上網已經有好多資訊，出面啲course 都係搵本書照抄，係叫做有個地方比自己實踐下。<br />\n<br />\n你想學飲好簡單，睇完書落酒吧試。<br />\n想學整就自己買套工具慢慢玩。"},{"pid":"e3414e4cccfd9ec3555355268c3fa46c4fd12394","tid":225133,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實上網已經有好多資訊，出面啲course 都係搵本書照抄，係叫做有個地方比自己實踐下。<br />\n<br />\n你想學飲好簡單，睇完書落酒吧試。<br />\n想學整就自己買套工具慢慢玩。</blockquote><br />\n傻豬黎<br />\n其實手法先係最重要<br />\n同一支酒，同樣份量<br />\n你 shaking 同 stirring 技巧唔一樣<br />\n出到黎既味道係完全唔同"},{"pid":"420d4b58a125d3eeac9e357ff85414053fd65958","tid":225133,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實上網已經有好多資訊，出面啲course 都係搵本書照抄，係叫做有個地方比自己實踐下。<br />\n<br />\n你想學飲好簡單，睇完書落酒吧試。<br />\n想學整就自己買套工具慢慢玩。</blockquote><br />\n傻豬黎<br />\n其實手法先係最重要<br />\n同一支酒，同樣份量<br />\n你 shaking 同 stirring 技巧唔一樣<br />\n出到黎既味道係完全唔同</blockquote><br />\nshaking定stirring雞尾酒recipe一定會講明<br />\n想學技巧嘅, 上網大把片"},{"pid":"3cf437e213718af39c7c2c84d10c5a573e7681b4","tid":225133,"uid":24808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"d用具可以係邊到買到？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c390f648efcbfb1ba02a4dca5faff1759bfb0e2","tid":225133,"uid":100943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d用具可以係邊到買到？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTaobao有 可以試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c581834ad3a5956ee2f7330fc3e486dd0d18b19","tid":225133,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d用具可以係邊到買到？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTaobao有 可以試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶啲質素差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603cc5d86bea921d84004c8b1b284fbc4b2648c4","tid":225133,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"Lmgtfy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aab3331741f7d825ce335590bd1336f5c0d0f5","tid":225133,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>d用具可以係邊到買到？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTaobao有 可以試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶啲質素差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粗用去住上海街先啦, 起碼有實物<br />\n少少哋買咗shaker(就算日本貨500ml/中size好少超過$160), 吧匙, 量杯同冰隔先<br />\n講究啲嘅上網買, 好多都有套裝賣<br />\n台灣有mixology米絲阿樂局<br />\nAmazon US同JP平貴都有<br />\n最靚嗰啲去美國Cocktail Kingdom, 日本就Bar Times, 不過唔知寄唔寄香港<br />\n<br />\n我淨係去過上海街買shaker同吧匙, 上面啲網站未幫襯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1c2be8756b26ef972111fa140121a2b4ae2a7d","tid":225133,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"另外shaker有分Boston(兩件頭)同Cobbler(三件頭)<br />\nBoston喺香港酒吧好常見, 見到個bartender將兩隻杯&quot;cup&quot;埋, 手枕兜嘢拍落去然後開始搖嗰啲就係用緊Boston<br />\nCobbler香港都有酒吧用, 多數係日式酒吧"},{"pid":"253f75648e1cf4cbb99433ceef4fbe85bed66c1c","tid":225133,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a73a002d4fb236f165d8eee4db4f5103958b32","tid":225133,"uid":64798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hksbtc.com/course.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksbtc.com%2Fcourse.html&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=52cbdb0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksbtc.com/course.html</a>"},{"pid":"712b5702e4f64ba241502eaaf9993f6895d5e88c","tid":225133,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實上網已經有好多資訊，出面啲course 都係搵本書照抄，係叫做有個地方比自己實踐下。<br />\n<br />\n你想學飲好簡單，睇完書落酒吧試。<br />\n想學整就自己買套工具慢慢玩。</blockquote><br />\n傻豬黎<br />\n其實手法先係最重要<br />\n同一支酒，同樣份量<br />\n你 shaking 同 stirring 技巧唔一樣<br />\n出到黎既味道係完全唔同</blockquote><br />\nshaking定stirring雞尾酒recipe一定會講明<br />\n想學技巧嘅, 上網大把片</blockquote><br />\n唔同嘅shake法同stir 嘅時間都會對味道有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=